FT  23 JUN 92 / Asil Nadir trial to start next year
THE TRIAL of Mr Asil Nadir, former chairman of Polly Peck International, and
Mr John Turner, group chief accountant, will start at the Old Bailey on
March 8 next year.
Mr Nadir faces 20 counts of theft for amounts totalling Pounds 30m. Mr
Turner faces 10 counts of false accounting. A further preparatory hearing
will be held in September.
